OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,FIn 2024, most of the Israeli attacks
OL,7,Fwere on areas more directly associated
OL,8,Fwith Hezbollah. Now the strikes are
OL,9,Fhappening in more random areas, each
OL,10,Fone eroding the sense of safety.
OL,12,FI spoke with the Lebanese Deputy Prime
OL,13,FMinister today. He had just come back
OL,14,Ffrom meeting with families displaced
OL,15,Ffrom the south of the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
