OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773843069
OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,FSome of the women asked him if their
OL,7,Fvillage still existed or if the bombs
OL,8,Ffrom Israel had destroyed it. "What
OL,9,Fcould I tell them? I said that to the
OL,10,Fbest of my knowledge it was, but who
OL,11,Fknows, I told them, let's hope you can
OL,12,Freturn to your homes, but knowing very
OL,13,Fwell that they may never be able to
OL,14,Fget back."
OL,16,FHe describes what is going on in the
OL,17,Fsouth as the systematic destruction of
OL,18,Fan entire area with the consequential
OL,19,Fdisplacement.
OL,26,@pD@_OUvD@JO]
