OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,F"Expelling people from their homes
OL,7,Funder the pretext of protecting their
OL,8,Flives is a war crime," he says, though
OL,9,Fit is clear he has little hope of any
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FTalking to ITV News' Emma Murphy,
OL,13,FLebanon's Deputy PM said 'expelling
OL,14,Fpeople from their homes in the pretext
OL,15,Fof protecting their lives is a war
OL,16,Fcrime'
OL,18,FTarek Mitri is a man trying to hold on
OL,19,Fto a belief in the rules-based order.
OL,20,FBut he is watching it slip away at the
OL,21,Fcost of his countrymen and women.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
