OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,F"You know, in international
OL,7,Fhumanitarian law, the Geneva
OL,8,FConvention and the protocols which
OL,9,Felaborate further, there are two basic
OL,10,Fprinciples.
OL,12,F"The principle of distinction,
OL,13,Fdistinguishing between combatants and
OL,14,Fcivilians, and the principle of
OL,15,Fproportion and proportionality. And
OL,16,FIsrael, through and through, is not
OL,17,Frespecting either of those two
OL,18,Fprinciples."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
