OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,FHe cites the death toll: one hundred
OL,7,Fchildren in two weeks. More than 800
OL,8,Fdead in total, 800,000 displaced.
OL,10,FHe fears this will be a long war and
OL,11,Ftakes threats by Israeli ministers
OL,12,Fseriously to turn parts of Lebanon
OL,13,Finto the same rubble as Gaza.
