OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,FThere is another parallel he draws.
OL,7,F"If the war objective of the Israelis
OL,8,Fis to disarm Hezbollah, to make
OL,9,FHezbollah surrender, well, taking this
OL,10,Fwould take years, not months."
OL,12,FThe Lebanese government is tasked with
OL,13,Fdisarming Hezbollah. He accepts it is
OL,14,Fnot something that is being done at
OL,15,Fpace but slowly and surely.
OL,17,FThe weakness of the Lebanese armed
OL,18,Fforces compared to the military might
OL,19,Fof Hezbollah is one stumbling block;
OL,20,Fthe continued presence of Israeli jets
OL,21,Fis another.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@^O]
