OL,3,CLebanon's deputy PM tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cfears country faces prolonged war
OL,6,FThose are not explanations that will
OL,7,Fsit easily with the international
OL,8,Fcommunity.
OL,10,FThere is an exhaustion here with the
OL,11,Fcontinual sense of jeopardy, the risk
OL,12,Fand reality of war. Israel and
OL,13,FAmerica's war with Iran has only
OL,14,Fincreased the dangers for this country
OL,15,Fand its people.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
